channel.description: [center][img]http://cyberducksmc.nn.pe/forums/images/logo.gif[/img] [img]http://oi43.tinypic.com/ejab13.jpg[/img] Forums: http://cyberducksmc.nn.pe/ [b]Welcome to CyberDucks! A new minecraft survival server. (W.I.P)[/b][/center] We're still fiddling with some things, but the server is now open to the public. Apart from a big friendly community, we're looking for some builders to build us some snazzy things, some redstone-ee people to do things with the builderee people. =-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-==-=-=-==-=-=-=-=-=-=-==-=-=-=-==-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-==-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-==-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-==-=-=-=-=-=-= Server has a plugins board in-game, but here are some of the main ones. Authme - Safe login plugin, so when you join the server for the first time, you register with a password which you then use to log into the server every time you join back. Factions - Create your own factions and claim land. Jobs - Earn money,titles and levels with specific jobs. =-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-==-=-=-=-=-=-==-=-=-=-=-=-=-==-=-=-==-=-=-=-=-=-=-==-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-==-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-==-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-==-=-=-=-=-=-= Server Rules: 1. No griefing. 2. No spamming. 3. No asking for ranks. 4. No 1x1 towers. 5. No floating trees. 6. Obey the staff and their law. 7. With that, do not argue with staff. 8. Respect all players.Have fun on our server! =-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-==-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-==-=-=-==-=-=-=-=-=-=-==-=-=-==-=-=-=-=-=-=-==-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-==-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-==-=-=-=-=-=-=
